graph TB
    URL[input URL or file path] --> DISP[load_html_doc_no_redirect dispatch by scheme then extension]

    DISP -->|http and html and htm and default| HTML[load_lambda_html_doc]
    DISP -->|svg and png and jpg and gif| IMG[load_dom_backed_image_document generates html body img]
    DISP -->|xml| XML[load_xml_doc needs xml-stylesheet else falls to text]
    DISP -->|json yaml txt csv and more| TEXT[load_text_doc wraps source in pre]
    DISP -->|ls| LS[load_lambda_script_doc runs script retains Runtime]
    DISP -->|pdf| PDF[load_pdf_bridge_doc in-memory ls bridge]
    DISP -->|tex and latex| TEX[load_latex_doc package render standalone html]
    DISP -->|md and markdown| MD[load_markdown_doc plus math subflow]
    DISP -->|wiki| WIKI[load_wiki_doc]

    IMG --> HTML
    PDF --> LS

    HTML --> ELEM[Lambda Element tree]
    XML --> ELEM
    TEXT --> ELEM
    LS --> ELEM
    TEX --> ELEM
    MD --> ELEM
    WIKI --> ELEM

    ELEM --> DDC[dom_document_create]
    DDC --> BDT[build_dom_tree_from_element retained DomElement tree]
    BDT --> CSS[collect stylesheets then optional scripts then CSS cascade]
    CSS --> DD[DomDocument ready]
    DD --> LR[shared layout_html_doc]
    LR --> RN[shared render_html_doc RAD_13]
